### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### List events
GET http://localhost:4000/api/events

### Create event
POST http://localhost:4000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "production",
  "orderId": "ORDER-123",
  "startDate": "2026-01-08",
  "endDate": "2026-01-08",
  "totalMinutes": 240,
  "travelMinutes": 0,
  "employeeIds": ["emp-1"]
}

### Update event
# Replace <ID> with a real event id from list events
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/events/<ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "production",
  "orderId": "ORDER-123",
  "startDate": "2026-01-09",
  "endDate": "2026-01-09",
  "totalMinutes": 300,
  "travelMinutes": 0,
  "employeeIds": ["emp-1"]
}

### Delete event
# Replace <ID> with a real event id
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/events/<ID>

### Capacity (remaining minutes)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/capacity?kind=production&date=2026-01-08

### Run AutoPlan
POST http://localhost:4000/api/autoplan/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-01-08",
  "endDate": "2026-01-31",
  "includeProduction": true,
  "includeMontage": true,
  "overwriteExisting": false
}

### Dashboard metrics
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/metrics?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31

### Dashboard KPIs
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/kpis?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31
